{"tid":2046422,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"中四生涉貼文宣被控 控方要求宵禁兼禁足 鄧少雄裁判官斥：本末倒置違反法律原則","createTime":"2020-06-01T11:44:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T02:31:54.000Z","uid":240362,"like":509,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":76,"replies":[{"pid":"ed161d3e8695065931904bf95a6d6903208afcb0","tid":2046422,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:44:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200601/VSF5FYWU7Z3ZP3XOK7SLWOOAAE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200601%2FVSF5FYWU7Z3ZP3XOK7SLWOOAAE%2F&d=f5Yas2EExEus6787o4Ns86zbj60slk4H2lWqI%2F1XlBQ%3D&h=fdf46061\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200601%2FVSF5FYWU7Z3ZP3XOK7SLWOOAAE%2F&h=7ab8f6cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/20200601/VSF5FYWU7Z3ZP3XOK7SLWOOAAE/</a><br />\n<br />\n16歲中四男生涉於昨日在沙田某隧道噴膠貼文宣，被控刑事毀壞及管有物品意圖損壞財產兩罪，今遭押解上沙田裁判法院提訊。控方不反對案件押後期間被告保釋，但要求法庭頒下宵禁令及禁足令等嚴格的擔保條件。<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">署理主任裁判官鄧少雄認為控方此舉形同將擔保條件作為懲罰或令被告造成負擔，違反法律原則，相關要求實屬本末倒置，最終未有批准控方申請。</span></strong>被告獲准以2,000元保釋，其間不得離港、須在指定地點居住，並且每周向警署報到一次。"},{"pid":"b5606728f2adc33f016b6176953f99394d6b168a","tid":2046422,"uid":51271,"like":108,"dislike":1,"score":107,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:45:04.000Z","msg":"根本不成比例，隨時只砌得入1500"},{"pid":"a2c919ef68686bc8059b05336b3a5be4b4b23c24","tid":2046422,"uid":273703,"like":98,"dislike":5,"score":93,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:45:36.000Z","msg":"制裁近了"},{"pid":"2b3b1d007dbf83685778d284ed9421822933de65","tid":2046422,"uid":57674,"like":144,"dislike":4,"score":140,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:47:03.000Z","msg":"制裁近了 開始扮返下野"},{"pid":"58565a4b336f334af3a87a14548e2e34097141a1","tid":2046422,"uid":21470,"like":68,"dislike":1,"score":67,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-01T11:47:41.000Z","msg":"睇唔透，極左官去晒邊？<br />\n辛苦啦手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\